text: Dominique Le Mèner (born November 12, 1958) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Sarthe department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
